message.content: "cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR". The paper deals with visual question answering and image captioning, which are both sub-fields of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also uses machine learning techniques to improve performance, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with ranking images and captions based on their relevance.
